            <title>[HIVE-12046] Re-create spark client if connection is dropped</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-12046</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, if the connection to the spark cluster is dropped, the spark client will stay in a bad state. A new Hive session is needed to re-establish the connection. It is better to auto reconnect in this case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
